    "Its effectiveness in teaching and learning STEM topics is attributed to its synthesis of modeling, visualization, and programming capabilities (Ziatdinov & Valles, 2022).",
    "Empirical studies indicate that students using GeoGebra achieve higher scores in mathematical modeling skills compared to their counterparts who do not use the software (Latifi et al., 2022).",
